"center\"|22\n| October 5, 2015\n|-\n| ''Last Man Standing: The Complete Fifth Season''\n| align=\"center\"|22\n| rowspan=\"2\"|June 26, 2018\n|-\n| ''Last Man Standing: The Complete Sixth Season''\n| align=\"center\"|22\n|}\n\n==Syndication==\nOn September 3, 2015, it was announced that [[Freeform (TV channel)|ABC Family]] (now Freeform) had obtained syndication rights to the series, which began airing episodes on September 28, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.sitcomsonline.com/2015/09/abc-family-fall-2015-schedule-with-last.html|title=ABC Family Fall 2015 Schedule with Last Man Standing; Girl Meets World Tackles Asperger's Syndrome in Upcoming Episode \u2013 SitcomsOnline.com News Blog|work=sitcomsonline.com}}</ref> As of 2018, Freeform no longer airs the series. On May 15, 2015, it was announced that [[Hallmark Channel]] had obtained the rights to the sitcom, and they aired the series from January 2016 until December 31, 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.sitcomsonline.com/2015/05/hallmark-channel-acquires-last-man.html|title=Hallmark Channel Acquires Last Man Standing for 2016; Sitcom Stars on Talk Shows (Week of May 18, 2015) \u2013 SitcomsOnline.com News Blog|work=sitcomsonline.com}}</ref> On September 4, 2015, the series joined the [[Country Music Television|CMT]] Network with a mini-marathon of episodes. The series also joined [[WGN America]] on April 30, 2018. <!-- The series also joined [[TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS]] on November 5, 2018. (comment hidden as it's unreferenced and refers to a future date)--> Currently, all eight seasons are available for streaming on [[Hulu]].\n\n==Broadcast==\n''Last Man Standing'' aired on ABC in the U.S.;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2011/05/abc-unveils-2011-12-primetime-schedule-132846/|title=ABC Primetime Schedule 2011|last=|first=|date=May 17, 2011|website=|access-date=May 27, 2017}}</ref> on [[Fox8]],\n[[Network Ten]] and [[Eleven (TV channel)|Eleven]] (previously aired on [[One (Australian TV channel)|One]]) in Australia;<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2013/09/fox8-premieres-sept-oct.html|title=FOX8 premieres: Sept / Oct|first=David|last=Knox|work=TV Tonight|date=September 20, 2013|accessdate=March 5, 2014}}</ref> [[City (TV network)|City]] in Canada; and [[TV3 (New Zealand)|TV3]] in New Zealand.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv3.co.nz/Shows/LastManStanding.aspx|title=Last Man Standing \u2013 Shows \u2013 TV3|work=MediaWorks|date=September 20, 2013|accessdate=March 5, 2014}}</ref>\n\nIn the United Kingdom and Ireland, it premiered on October 9, 2012 on [[Sky One]],<ref name=tvwise>{{cite web|title=Sky1 Acquires UK Rights To ABC's Comedy Series 'Last Man Standing'|url=http://www.tvwise.co.uk/2012/09/sky1-acquires-uk-rights-to-abcs-comedy-series-last-man-standing/|first=Patrick|last=Munn|work=TVWise|date=September 19, 2012|accessdate=September 19, 2012}}</ref> which aired the first three seasons before dropping it due to low ratings; the show was bought by [[E4 (TV channel)|E4]], where it premiered on March 13, 2017;<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chortle.co.uk/news/2017/03/03/26999/e4_buys_last_man_standing|title=E4 buys Last Man Standing|date=March 3, 2017|work=[[Chortle]]|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref> [[Channel 4]] then reran the program on Sunday mornings from July until September 2017; in 2018, [[5Star]] acquired the show for reruns and new episodes.\n\nIn [[Israel]], it airs on [[yes (Israel)|yes Comedy]].{{citation needed|date=July 2018}}\n\nIn [[the Netherlands]], it is on [[RTL 7]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tvgids.net/ |website=TV GIDS |title=TV GIDS Nederland |access-date=March 20, 2019 |language=nl }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}<!--\n<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/11/arts/television/last-man-standing-uses-an-experienced-stable-of-writers.html?_r=0 |title=\"'Last Man Standing' Uses an Experienced Stable of Writers\" |work=New York Times |date=January 9, 2015 |accessdate=August 3, 2015 }}</ref>\n -->\